OL,3,CPPS rules out soldier prosecutions
OL,4,Cover deaths of girl and man
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's Public Prosecution
OL,7,FService has ruled out prosecuting two
OL,8,Fsoldiers in connection with the
OL,9,Fseparate deaths of a 14-year-old girl
OL,10,Fand a 41-year-old man.
OL,12,FAnnette McGavigan and William
OL,13,FMcGreanery were shot in separate
OL,14,Fincidents in Londonderry in 1971.
OL,16,FFollowing investigations the PSNI
OL,17,Fsubmitted files for consideration to
OL,18,Fthe PPS for consideration.
