OL,4,Cover deaths of girl and man
OL,6,FThe PPS said it had determined that
OL,7,Fbased on the available evidence in
OL,8,Fboth cases there was insufficient to
OL,9,Fprovide a reasonable prospect of
OL,10,Fconviction".
OL,12,FOne former soldier, known as Soldier
OL,13,FA, was reported on an investigation
OL,14,Ffile in connection with the death of
OL,15,FWilliam McGreanery in the early hours
OL,16,Fof 15 September 1971.
