OL,6,FA second former soldier, known as
OL,7,FSoldier B, was reported in connection
OL,8,Fwith the shooting of 14-year-old
OL,9,FAnnette McGavigan during unrest in
OL,10,FDerry on 6 September 1971.
OL,12,FPPS Assistant Director Martin Hardy
OL,13,Fsaid they has "carefully considered
OL,14,Fall the evidence reported in
OL,15,Fconnection with both cases".
