OL,6,F"Both cases featured significant
OL,7,Fevidential difficulties arising from
OL,8,Fthe circumstances in which accounts
OL,9,Fwere taken and recorded, both by the
OL,10,FRoyal Military Police in 1971, and
OL,11,Flater by the PSNI's Historical
OL,12,FEnquiries Team.J"In addition, the
OL,13,Fdeath of significant witnesses and a
OL,14,Ffailure to conduct effective
OL,15,Finvestigations at the time has
OL,16,Fundoubtedly hampered more recent
OL,17,Finvestigative efforts and the
OL,18,Fprosecutorial prospects in these
OL,19,Fcases."
