OL,6,F"As difficult as these outcomes will
OL,7,Fbe for the families of those killed,
OL,8,Fwe have offered assurances that we
OL,9,Fhave taken these decisions only after
OL,10,Fa thorough and impartial consideration
OL,11,Fof all the available evidence and
OL,12,Frelevant legal issues and in line with
OL,13,Fthe Code for Prosecutors."
